## Unit 1 Day 8-9: Impact of Computers and Communication

Pull out your curriculum book and look at the lesson for Unit 1, day 8-9 on page 39.

<a href="http://www.exploringcs.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/ExploringComputerScience-v5.0.pdf#page=39" target="_blank">Access a digital copy of the lesson >></a>

#### Key Concepts

1. Describe the impact of digital communication on society

1. Identify privacy issues caused by digital communication

#### Common Difficulties

Students may not remember a time before digital communication and will need additional time and resources to understand concepts covered by this lesson.

#### PD Outline

The following outline lists the topics covered on each level of this stage. <i>This online PD is intended to be a companion to the ECS curriculum. Have your book open as you go through the levels of this stage.</i>

